{"tid":1395033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂 其實都過咗五年啦 重唔夠耐咩?","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:03:56.000Z","uid":220864,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40cad73de267f28513175ca613118cab9d566182","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"喂你自己禁入去wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%9C%9F%E6%99%AE%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2581%25B8&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=33c3f36d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%9C%9F%E6%99%AE%E9%81%B8</a><br />\n睇下真普選呢一頁<br />\n14年之後有咩更新?<br />\n<br />\n呢排成日見到d人係到話<br />\n真普選係要長期抗爭<br />\n又話最起碼2022先有啦<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔撚明<br />\n14年個時,大家都無而家呢一刻咁團結<br />\n咁有火咁有決心<br />\n點解大家重唔可以一齊去爭取一樣原本係屬於我的嘅野?<br />\n<br />\n今次輸咗<br />\n我都唔知下次抗爭係點<br />\n我都可能以後安份守己繼續做個打工仔<br />\n第時老個陣可能有普選嘅<br />\n不過新移民都佔過半數<br />\n個票都唔知係咪代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n我好想見到香港人齊上齊落<br />\n一齊下定決心,一日無真普選,我地點都唔會收手<br />\n不自由毋寧死<br />\n一係真普選<br />\n一係你出老解開真槍射死我地<br />\n咁認命<br />\n<br />\n我知我呢個要求係好高好天真<br />\n但係香港人<br />\n你地肯覺醒未<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我知大家一定會講,救義士先係我地首要嘅訴求,我絕對同意,但係我覺得救到佢地唯一的方法,就係真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n純粹放負,呢邊日日出街見到狗都好撚想打"},{"pid":"f240dcb8ac94abae46cb7b97ef180df267f57bf9","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"對於2022年先有真普選個班人<br />\n我嘅回應係<br />\n落實咗真普選<br />\n林鄭即刻落台<br />\n其實就已經可以推行<br />\n<br />\n雖然一切好理想<br />\n但係你諗都唔敢諗?<br />\n你會有飛機搭?"},{"pid":"9e2ae53a8736b3b3d37bfaa398a3d3df07b87580","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec7e0776a7c2d8be7fa048128e48c8d8f0ace9","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"應該都無咩人睇到<br />\n留番係到<br />\n等我自己一個第時回味下都好"},{"pid":"d5779756112feefdc4a2b9c317adfb1b224ce22a","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89eaca79190b1abcf18fc1b834e6ea616866fb8","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a4c6d958fe36e0eee1a65f244e0478361f5422","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbeb78009f8cc9c68230c87f6427c1c3c2d9b6cd","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd6ce2ac7455842417d63a6f43ddd41e9206cb6","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d6362b68503af923b9f9ab933fd486d82162ec","tid":1395033,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b1fe7f8f780fa5d69b9417c2539372a2b103592","tid":1395033,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff939a3b4f434032fc011a73747fc712b283d73a","tid":13950